# FinTrack AI — Frontend Patterns

## 1. tRPC — only data layer, no fetch/axios

```typescript
// ✅ Query
const { data, isLoading } = trpc.category.list.useQuery();

// ✅ Mutation
const mut = trpc.transaction.create.useMutation({ onSuccess: () => { ... } });

// ❌ Never use fetch() or axios for app data
```

## 2. Invalidate all affected queries after mutations

After any transaction create / update / delete, invalidate the full set:

```typescript
const utils = trpc.useUtils();

// After transaction mutation:
utils.transaction.list.invalidate();
utils.category.list.invalidate();
utils.report.monthly.invalidate();
utils.report.yoy.invalidate();
utils.report.budgetStatus.invalidate();

// Then recalc budgets:
recalcBudgetsMutation.mutate();
```

Missing an invalidation = stale data on other pages until manual refresh.

## 3. Money input — vi-VN thousand separators

```typescript
// Display with separators; store raw number
function fmtNum(val: string): string {
  const raw = val.replace(/[^0-9]/g, "");
  return raw ? parseInt(raw, 10).toLocaleString("vi-VN") : "";
}
function parseNum(val: string): number {
  return parseFloat(val.replace(/\./g, "").replace(/,/g, "")) || 0;
}
```

## 4. Use shared utilities — never re-implement

```typescript
import { formatVND, formatVNDShort, formatDate, todayString,
         getCurrentMonthYear, ensureNumber, getBudgetProgressColor } from "@/lib/utils";
```

- `formatVND(n)` — full VNĐ with separators
- `formatVNDShort(n)` — compact (tr / k)
- `todayString()` — today as `"YYYY-MM-DD"`
- `ensureNumber(v)` — safe Number() with 0 fallback
- Never call `new Intl.NumberFormat(...)` directly in page components

## 5. Routing — wouter only

```typescript
import { Link, useLocation } from "wouter";
// ❌ Never import from react-router-dom
```

## 6. Toasts — sonner only

```typescript
import { toast } from "sonner";
toast.success("Đã lưu");
toast.error(e.message);
// ❌ Never use window.alert() or custom toast
```

## 7. Page layout pattern

Every new page must be wrapped by `DashboardLayout` automatically (via `App.tsx` routes). Do not add a second layout wrapper inside a page component.

```typescript
// New page template
export default function MyNewPage() {
  return (
    <div className="p-3 sm:p-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-4">
      <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Page Title</h1>
      {/* content */}
    </div>
  );
}
```
